    <div class="sub">Eden's Generation — Ages 5–14</div>
    <p>33 illustrated narratives from Genesis to Revelation for young hearts.</p>
    <span class="badge">Ages 5–14</span>
  </a>
  <a href="standard.html" class="card edition-standard">
    <div class="icon">📖</div><h2>The Standard AKJV</h2>
    <div class="sub">The Universal Edition — Ships with Alfred Linux</div>
